app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
  console.error(err.stack); // Log internally
  res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal server error' }); // Reveal nothing
});
```

### 7. Hardcoded Port / No Environment Configuration

Port `3000` is hardcoded with no `.env` support. Secrets (when added) are likely to end up hardcoded too.

**Recommendation:**

```js
